<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12157</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25580</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猫咪又藏在汤姆的口袋里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25581</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29866</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>德克倒在了椅子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29867</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34089</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他看上去不太好。”汤姆想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34090</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39305</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，德克的女儿进来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39306</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42625</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她端着一个盘子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42626</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47848</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“尝一点牛奶和吐司，父亲。”安说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47849</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53865</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>德克捂着肚子难过地说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53866</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在这里当大管家太不容易了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59320</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66098</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在还有龙来袭击皇宫！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66099</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72650</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>安拍着他的肩膀说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“尝一点牛奶和吐司吧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83375</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>吃了会舒服些的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83376</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88923</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆走过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88924</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91030</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您需要帮忙吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91031</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94399</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不用！”德克瞪着汤姆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94400</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102659</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的女儿才应该是皇家魔法师。不是你！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102660</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109081</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“父亲。”安温柔地说，“我并不想做......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109082</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115760</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你总有一天会做皇家魔法师的。”德克厉声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115761</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119504</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得回屋顶去了。”德克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119505</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124854</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他放下牛奶离开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124855</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130628</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130629</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133264</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的父亲讨厌我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133265</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138572</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为他希望我做皇家魔法师。”安说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138573</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143587</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得你是个很棒的魔法师了，汤姆。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143588</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145795</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆摇摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145796</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149057</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，我不是好魔法师。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149058</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151848</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你很棒的。”安说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151849</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154661</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“给我看一下你的魔法吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154662</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161272</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧。”汤姆挥动了魔杖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161273</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>噗！玫瑰出现了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165404</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆笑了，把玫瑰给了安。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177165</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你看吧？”安说，“谢谢。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177166</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179892</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不客气。”汤姆说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179893</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185981</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要去跟龙战斗了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>